## Button Colors

**Rule**: Selection buttons (teams, weekdays, slots, etc.) use blue color. Exceptions: Save, Cancel, Add Entry, and Delete buttons use their default/semantic colors.

### CORRECT Patterns:

**Selection Buttons (Blue)**:
```tsx
// Team selection, weekday selection, slot selection, etc.
<Button className={cn(
  isSelected ? 'bg-blue-600 text-white' : 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-700'
)}>
  {team}
</Button>
```

**Action Buttons (Default/Semantic Colors)**:
```tsx
// Save button - use primary/default
<Button type="submit">Save</Button>

// Cancel button - use outline variant
<Button variant="outline" onClick={onCancel}>Cancel</Button>

// Add entry button - use default
<Button onClick={handleAdd}>
  <Plus className="h-4 w-4 mr-2" />
  Add New Entry
</Button>

// Delete button - use destructive variant
<Button variant="destructive" onClick={handleDelete}>
  <Trash2 className="h-4 w-4" />
</Button>
```

### WRONG Pattern:
```tsx
// Don't use black/primary for selection buttons
<Button className={cn(isSelected ? 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground' : '')}>
  {option}
</Button>
```

