## Tooltip Background Color

**Rule**: Tooltip background color should be white.

### CORRECT Pattern:
```tsx
// In tooltip component or when styling tooltips
<div className="px-2 py-1 text-xs text-popover-foreground bg-white border border-border rounded-md shadow-md">
  {tooltipContent}
</div>
```

**Note**: If using a Tooltip component from the UI library, ensure it uses `bg-white` or `bg-popover` (if popover background is white) instead of dark backgrounds.

