## Summary Checklist

When creating new UI components, ensure:

- [ ] Small icons use lucide-react icons (not emojis)
- [ ] Selection buttons use blue color (`bg-blue-600 text-white` when selected)
- [ ] Action buttons (Save, Cancel, Add, Delete) use appropriate semantic variants
- [ ] Toggle buttons have circular thumb, text inside track, appropriate width
- [ ] Dialog width matches content (default to `max-w-lg`, allow text wrapping)
- [ ] Tooltips use white background
